commit.message:
Upgrade python 3 (#62)

* Upgrade python2 to python3 and add parens to print calls

* Update dockerfile for python3

* Upgrade pip to pip3

* Remove unicode strings and change unicodecsv to csv

* Move to python3 absolute imports

* convert filter to list for Python3 filter() behavior

* Fix utf-8 file encoding errors

* Run yapf on python code

* Remove unicode Python 2 related imports

* reformat with yapf 0.21.0

* Remove explicit unicode strings

* Add additional 2to3 suggestions

* Reformat utils

* Write training data directly to file instead of piping through stdout

* Revert tokenizer consolidation into utils

* Revert Dockerfile reorder

* Revert changes to print output

* Write directly to stdout instead of using print()

* Fix test evaluation

* Use pip install to require Python 3 from setup.py

* Respond to PR comments

* Reformat code

* Use 10 decimal places

* Revert test changes

* Revert spacing change

Co-authored-by: William <William Edmisten>
